## Routing Logic

| Input | Modes to Run |
|-------|-------------|
| URL only | A + C, offer D |
| Keyword only | D, offer B |
| Raw content pasted | A + B |
| "Audit my SEO" | All four modes |
| Missing target keyword | Ask before running A or B |

